Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy applies to all applications and games (hereinafter referred to as "Application") created by Trimatra Studio (hereinafter referred to as "Service Provider"). This service is provided "AS IS" and is available for use under the terms described herein.
By downloading or using the Application, you agree to this Privacy Policy, which discloses how we collect, use, and manage user data.
Information Collection and Use
The Application collects certain data to provide better services, improve functionality, and personalize your experience. The types of data collected include:
Device Information:
Such as IP address, operating system, device model, and browser type.
Usage Data:
Pages visited within the Application, duration of usage, and interaction logs.
Location Data:
Approximate geographical location to enhance features such as personalized content and analytics.
We use collected data to:
Improve user experience and Application functionality.
Deliver personalized recommendations.
Analyze trends and monitor usage statistics.
Log Files
The Application records log files, which include IP addresses, browser types, ISPs, date/time stamps, and referring/exit pages. These are used to:
Diagnose technical issues.
Analyze user trends and behaviors.
Enhance security and prevent misuse.
